description:
Danny welcomes Jay Manuel from America's Next Top Model to Everything Iconic. They discuss his time on the show, the decision to leave, behind the scenes, and SO much more! They also discuss his new book, The Wig, The Bitch and the Meltdown.


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
